{"word":"G4340 - πρόσκαιρος - próskairos - pros'-kahee-ros - Dur- for awhile","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρόσκαιρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">próskairos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros'-kahee-ros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Dur- for awhile</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கொஞ்சகால, அதிசீக்கிர, அந்நித்யமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"for a season, enduring only for a while, temporary"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G2540 - καιρός - kairós - kahee-ros'/2540\">G2540</a>; <i>for</i> the <i>occasion</i> only, that is, <i>temporary:</i> - dur- [eth] for awhile, endure for a time, for a season, temporal.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G170/170\">G170</a>, <a href=\"#/G171/171\">G171</a>, <a href=\"#/G2120/2120\">G2120</a>, <a href=\"#/G2121/2121\">G2121</a>, <a href=\"#/G2122/2122\">G2122</a>, <a href=\"#/G2540/2540\">G2540</a>, <a href=\"#/G4340/4340\">G4340</a>"}]}